=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36k1dcx\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36kfhj\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">从个人助理，到协作平台</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36kfhe\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">OpenAI 做群聊的真实原因，可能和大多数人想的不一样。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36kkag\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">答案不是模型遇到瓶颈，而是 OpenAI 的商业化逻辑在调整。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36k197k\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 明白了一件事：只卖 API，客户随时能换供应商。</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">而要真正留住用户，得让他们在你这儿沉淀关系和数据</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。就像我们离不开微信一样。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36k18xl\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span leaf=\"\">群聊就是按照这个思路，</span><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">把 ChatGPT 从个人助理变成了一个可协作的平台</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36kh4n\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">这样就产生了网络效应，当用户用 ChatGPT 不是因为模型出色，而是因为项目、客户在这时，这时候，用户离开的代价就不是换个 API 接口或者模型那么简单了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"image\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-backh=\"349\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6036977491961415\" data-w=\"2488\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5e56bbeb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F8cu01Kavc5YW76ONibsy6bzVfAxfpMsJVGxgibc00hD9a4viahapLN3kjpYicn0FNi