b(45, 113, 214);\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n          <p style=\"clear: both;min-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36kn83\"><em><strong mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></strong></em></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:17px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36kakg\"><span style=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-template&quot;:&quot;t&quot;,&quot;mpa-paragraph-type&quot;:&quot;title&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; text-align: center;&quot;,&quot;mpa-from-tpl&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mpa-is-content&quot;:&quot;t&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">多 Agent 协作的未来？</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36k7sr\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">再往远看，OpenAI 的群聊功能，很有可能在测试多 Agent 协作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36k9r1\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">想象一下不远的未来，当你在项目群里说：「咱们做个读书笔记 App」。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36kazk\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">然后 ChatGPT 们自动捕捉到这个信息，群里的 GPT 产品经理开始问需求、写 PRD，GPT 工程师同步列技术方案，GPT 设计师画原型，GPT 测试准备用例清单。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36kgg\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">它们互相讨论、互相挑刺，你只需要在关键节点拍板。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36klz7\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">听起来很科幻？但今天的群聊功能很有可能就是第一步。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36k10pf\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">单 AI 群聊，可能就是在为多 AI 协作，做第一步的技术验证和用户教育。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36k1xkf\"><span leaf=\"\">当单 Agent 能在多人场景里自然协作，多个 Agent 的分工配合也就不远了。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36k16p0\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">如果说微信定义了移动时代的沟通方式，那么 OpenAI，正在定义 AI 时代人与机器的协作范式。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36k1mw7\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\">当大部分人还在用 AI 总结会议记录时，OpenAI 已经让 AI 坐进了人类的会议室。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:25px 8px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;text-align:justify;\" mpa-paragraph-type=\"body\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;line-height:1.6;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mi76z36kb5i\"><span leaf=\"\">群聊功能，可能又是一个时代的转折。</span></strong></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深入分析了 OpenAI 群聊功能，认为其不仅是人机协作的升级，更是 OpenAI 从个人助理向协作平台转型的关键一步，并预示了多 Agent 协作的未来。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深入分析了 OpenAI 群聊功能，认为其不仅是人机协作的升级，更是 OpenAI 从个人助理向协作平台转型的关键一步，并预示了多 Agent 协作的未来。",
  "summary": "文章详细解读了 OpenAI 最新推出的群聊功能，指出其核心在于 AI 的“场景感知能力”，即 AI 能够主动判断何时介入对话，而非仅被动响应@指令。作者认为，这一功能并非简单的社交尝试，而是 OpenAI 商业化战略调整的重要体现，旨在通过沉淀用户关系和数据，将 ChatGPT 从单一的个人助理工具升级为具有网络效应的协作平台。文章进一步展望，该功能可能是 OpenAI 测试多 Agent 协作模式的初步尝试，为未来多个 AI 角色协同完成复杂任务奠定基础，最终可能重新定义 AI 时代的人机协作范式。",
